---
import { Bot, Mail, MapPin, Phone, Shield } from "@lucide/astro";
---

<footer class="bg-muted py-16">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
      {/* Logo and Description */}
      <div class="lg:col-span-2">
        <div class="flex items-center space-x-2 mb-4">
          <div class="flex items-center w-full max-w-[40px]">
            <img src="/icon.png" />
          </div>
          <span class="text-xl font-bold text-[primary]">Olivia</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground font-light mb-6 max-w-md text-pretty">
          A primeira IA brasileira especializada em reativar pacientes inativos
          de clínicas odontológicas. Tecnologia avançada com resultados
          comprovados.
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center space-x-4 text-sm text-muted-foreground">
          <div class="flex items-center">
            <Shield class="mr-2 h-4 w-4" />
            LGPD Compliant
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center">
            <span class="mr-2 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-green-500"></span>
            Sistema Ativo
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      {/* Contact */}
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-4">Contato</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm font-light text-muted-foreground">
          <li class="flex items-center">
            <Mail class="mr-2 h-4 w-4" />
            contato@useolivia.app
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center">
            <Phone class="mr-2 h-4 w-4" />
            (19) 9 2001-6741
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center">
            <MapPin class="mr-2 h-4 w-4" />
            São Paulo, SP
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div
      class="border-t mt-12 pt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-center text-sm text-muted-foreground"
    >
      <p>&copy; 2025 Olivia AI. Todos os direitos reservados.</p>
      <div class="flex space-x-6 mt-4 sm:mt-0">
        <a href="#" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">
          Política de Privacidade
        </a>
        <a href="#" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">
          Termos de Uso
        </a>
        <a href="#" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors"> LGPD </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
